ce:section.ce:para:
Fresh potatoes were cleaned, peeled, and sliced as described above, then randomly assigned to four treatments:

                                 (1)

CK: Immersed in deionized water for 15 min;


                                 (2)

Ca2
                                    + treatment: Immersed in a calcium lactate solution with a Ca2+ concentration of 2.44 mg/mL for 15 min;


                                 (3)

CQDs treatment: Immersed in a 1 mg/mL CQDs solution for 15 min;


                                 (4)

Ca-CQDs treatment: Immersed in a 1 mg/mL Ca-CQDs solution for 15 min.
